## Get Existing Location

> Example Request

```shell
curl <%=@api_prefix%>/2/locations/136 \
 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->get("locations/136");
?>
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "location": <%= print_json(data.objects['location'], :minimal=>true).indent(2) %>
}
```

### HTTP Request
`GET <%=@api_prefix%>/2/locations/{id}`

### Parameters

Key | Description
--- | -----------
id | ID of the location requested.


